sentences: Benjamin Arthur McKee (born April 7, 1985) is an American musician, songwriter, and record producer.
In 2009, McKee was invited by Wayne Sermon to join Imagine Dragons, based out of Las Vegas.

The band proceeded to earn a number of local accolades including "Best CD of 2011" (Vegas SEVEN), "Best Local Indie Band 2010" (Las Vegas Weekly), and "Las Vegas' Newest Must See Live Act" (Las Vegas CityLife).
